        <Parent_String>thermal insulation [300014878], insulation by function [300192869], insulation [300014871], building materials [300014857], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
